Class Ticket

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tickets.model.ticket.Ticket
public class Ticket extends Object
The ticket class holds information about each individual ticket, such as its name, owner, description, and whether or not it's active
Author:
John Eakes, Colin Fawcett
